aProfessor.bio:
Doctor Jihyo graduated from De La Salle University in 1990. Since then he's been teaching programming Courses
									at different universities in the country. Notably, he starred in a crime film named "Ang Ninong" as Michael De la Cruz. In 2020 ,
									he started teaching at De la Salle University in Manila.
